'''Senior clone commander''', also known simply as '''senior commander''', was the second highest [[Military rank/Legends|military rank]] that a [[Clone Commander/Legends|clone trooper commander]] could hold within the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]]. Distinguished by their [[Color/Legends|yellow]] [[Armor/Legends|armor]] flashes towards the beginning of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] between the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]], senior [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] [[Commander/Legends|commanders]] were placed in charge of [[Legion/Legends|legions]], also called [[Brigade/Legends|brigades]], alongside a [[Jedi General/Legends|Jedi General]].<ref name="TEGtW" />

In the Grand Army of the Republic's [[Order of Battle/Legends|Order of Battle]], senior clone commanders were subordinate to [[Clone Marshal Commander/Legends|clone marshal commanders]], while [[clone regimental commander]] were subordinate to [[Senior Commander/Legends|senior commanders]].<ref name="TEGtW" /> Notable senior clone commanders included Senior Commander [[Gree (clone trooper)/Legends|Gree]] of the [[41st Stormtrooper Legion|41st Elite Legion]]<ref name="Vehicles Collection 30">[[Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection 30|''Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection'' 30]]</ref> and Senior Commander [[A'den]] of the [[7th Legion]].<ref name="GGAR">{{InsiderCite|84|Guide to the Grand Army of the Republic}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The rank of senior clone commander was first mentioned in "[[Guide to the Grand Army of the Republic]]," an eight-page reference article written by [[Karen Traviss]] and [[Ryan Kaufman (real person)|Ryan Kaufman]] for the [[Star Wars Insider 84|84th issue]] of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'',<ref name="GGAR" /> published by [[IDG Entertainment]] on [[September 26]], [[2005]].<ref name="InsiderDate">{{SWArchive|url=community/fanclub/mag/news20050913.html|text=The Ultimate Clone Guide in ''Star Wars Insider'' #84}}</ref>

